      "description": "An entity, group, or organization that offers Incentive tokens for their respective Reward Vault with the goal of capturing $BGT emissions for their protocol and/or users",
      "capabilities": [
        "Create Reward Vault",
        "Submit governance proposal to whitelist Reward Vault",
        "Offer Incentive Tokens",
        "Manage Incentive Rates",
        "Deposit additional Incentive Tokens"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
